name: IAM-02_cBGR
description: v4w.enko - "IAM-02_cBGR" [Intermediate Algorithmic Multicomponent - 02_cBGR]  is the abstraction which connects intermediate cross-pattern`s instructions to demonstrate the multicomponent relationship of various geometric algorithms. Abstraction 02_cBGR is dedicated to the "Metaball", "Voronoi diagram" and "Delaunay triangulation" transformations as well. Colored in the palette of Blue, Green and Red (cBGR).  The patterns are transformated with diferent seeds and are linked in specific way to draw the algorithmic abstract artwork with each other. The energy of abstract processes in relationship of algorithms is linked. Eight charged points are divided in two groups and are transforming the space around. Packed as GIF. 1024*1024px / 121 frames.
